<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1037747" n="10v"/>
<p>Viro Clarissimo <choice><abbr>Joh.</abbr><expan>Johanni</expan></choice> Bernoull<choice><orig><g ref="#j">j</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice> Patruo suo <choice><abbr>pl.</abbr><expan>plurime</expan></choice> honorando S. P. D. <choice><abbr>N.</abbr><expan>Nicolaus</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>B.</abbr><expan>Bernoulli</expan></choice> </p>
<p>Intellexi non sine gaudio ex literis<!-- brieftag --> <rs key="pers_DE-588-135542286" type="person">Patris</rs> mei Deum <choice><abbr>O.</abbr><expan>Optimum</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>M.</abbr><expan>Maximum</expan></choice> familiam Tuam <rs key="pers_DE-588-117589136" type="person">filio</rs> auxisse, de quo pro<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>in Tibi et <rs key="pers_DE-588-108991332X" type="person">uxori</rs> Tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> animitus gratulor su<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>opere vovens, ut Deus eundem Tuum <rs key="pers_DE-588-117589136" type="person">filium</rs> recens na<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tum non solum per longam a<choice><orig><g ref="#nn">n̄</g></orig><reg>nn</reg></choice>orum seriem corpore et animo valentem conservare, sed et ita
                    <lb/>largiter Spiritus sui sancti donis instruere velit, ut dignus aliquando eruditionis, fam<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> et virtu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tum Paternarum heres existere queat. Permitte etiam, Patrue honoratissime, ut et mihi gra<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tuler ob auctum jam illorum numerum, quibus forte aliquando gratum, quem Tibi pro tot
                    <lb/>mihi exhibitis veri amoris argumentis debeo, animum ipso opere demonstrare potero. Sane
                    <lb/>non possum non singulari Tuo erga me amori tribuere, quod me Amicis tam serio co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>en<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>dare voluisti; multum certe valuit co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>endatio Tua apud <choice><abbr>Nob.</abbr><expan>Nobilissimum</expan></choice> Fatium<rs key="pers_DE-588-103763058" type="person"/>, et eam simili<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ter apud <choice><abbr>Ill.</abbr><expan>Illustrissimum</expan></choice> Abbatem <rs key="pers_DE-588-120052539" type="person">Bignonium</rs> et <choice><abbr>Cl.</abbr><expan>Clarissimum</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-119062372" type="person">Varignonium</rs> non exiguum pondus habituram
                    <lb/>esse persuasus sum. Valde humaniter me et lauto etiam convivio exceperunt <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-103763058" type="person">Fatius</rs>
<lb/>et <rs type="person">uxor</rs><!-- persontag --> ejus, ipse quoque una cum <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person">Rittero</rs><!-- persontag --> conditionem aliquam mihi comparare studuit, sed
                    <lb/>frustra. Salutant te quamplurimum ambo et <abbr>Cl.</abbr> etiam <abbr>Prof.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-104272538" type="person">Gautierius</rs>, qui ipse ante paucos
                    <lb/>dies me domi invisere dignatus fuit. Audivi hic <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> quodam<!-- persontag --> Gallo, qui cum <rs key="pers_DE-588-104185643" type="person">Burneto</rs> ob co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>unia
                    <lb/>studia <choice><orig><g ref="#klammerauf">|:</g></orig><reg>(</reg></choice>nam et ipse Theologi<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> et Mathesi addictus est<choice><orig><g ref="#klammerzu">:|</g></orig><reg>)</reg></choice> hactenus co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>ercium epistolicum ha<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>buit, illum in pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sens <rs key="place_GEO-2747373" type="place">Hag<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>-Comitum</rs> esse, miror itaque quod, dum per <rs key="place_KON-deutsch" type="place">Germaniam</rs> transiit
                    <lb/>nullas ad Te literas dederit; pergratum facies, si quod novi ab ipso vel ab <rs key="pers_DE-588-119112450" type="person">Hermanno</rs> audies
                    <lb/>mecum co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>unicare dignaberis. Adderem aliquid de monstro illo <rs type="person">Italico</rs><!-- persontag -->, nisi ejus recordatio
                    <lb/>Tibi tam molesta et odiosa esset; hoc unicum tamen tacere nequeo, me nempe maxime do<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>lere, operam Tuam in erudiendo tam ingrato et inutili terr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> pondere tam male colloca<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tam fuisse. Pro voto Tuo, quo mihi prosperum iter apprecaris, su<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>as ago gratias Deum
                    <pb facs="1037748" n="11r"/>
<lb/>vicissim rogans, ut clementer concedere velit, ut post absolutum iter in <rs key="place_VER-frankr" type="place">Galliam</rs>, quod isto mane
                    <lb/>sub Divina tutela aggrediar, domum redux Te Tuosque omnes exoptata fruentes valetudine
                    <lb/>conspicere et compellare queam. Vale igitur interim quamplurimum una cum <rs key="pers_DE-588-108991332X" type="person">Uxore</rs> et liberis<!-- persontag -->
<lb/>charissimis, meque Tibi porro de meliore nota co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>endatum habe. Genev<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> d. 10<choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice> Junii 1710.</p>
<postscript><p><abbr>P. S.</abbr> De Decanatu Philosophico, quem Tibi nunc altera vice delatum esse pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>ter omnem spem
                    <lb/>audivi, l<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>tus Tibi gratulor.</p></postscript>
</div>
